headline: State Street Corporation 2025 Annual Meeting of Shareholders
summary: BOSTON, May 09, 2025--As previously announced, State Street Corporation (NYSE:STT) will hold the 2025 Annual Meeting of Shareholders on Wednesday, May 14, 2025 at 9:00 a.m. ET. The Annual Meeting of Shareholders will be conducted online via live audio webcast at www.virtualshareholdermeeting.com/STT2025. State Street’s Chairman and Chief Executive Officer, Ronald P. O’Hanley, will provide brief remarks and respond to shareholder submitted questions.
